      <title><![CDATA[用JQuery实现文章打赏弹窗功能]]></title>
      <url>/2017/08/21/how-to-achieve-the-reward-function/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js"> </script><p>很多的博客的博主们都喜欢在每篇文章的底部加入一个打赏的功能，虽然不会有人真的给打赏一些小费，但它可以使博客的功能结构更加的丰富起来。况且读者是否打赏全凭个人心情决定，倘若你的文章勾勒出一点他/她的共鸣和感慨，那恭喜你，你已经有拥戴者了。</p>
<h3 id="step-1：-查看打赏效果"><a href="#step-1：-查看打赏效果" class="headerlink" title="step 1： 查看打赏效果"></a>step 1： 查看打赏效果</h3><p>请点击该文字<a href="#tips">底部</a>滑到底部，查看打赏功能效果。以确保是否喜欢该效果，同时为了把握整个功能的全貌。</p>
<h3 id="step-2：-编写打赏模块的代码"><a href="#step-2：-编写打赏模块的代码" class="headerlink" title="step 2： 编写打赏模块的代码"></a>step 2： 编写打赏模块的代码</h3><p><code>layout\_partial</code>下新建<code>donate.ejs</code>输入如下内容：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;p&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:void(0)&quot; class=&quot;dashang&quot; onclick=&quot;dashangToggle()&quot; title=&quot;打赏&quot;&gt;赞赏支持&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;/p&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;span class=&quot;donate_txt&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;%=theme.donate_message%&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;div class=&quot;shang_box&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:void(0)&quot; class=&quot;shang_close&quot; onclick=&quot;dashangToggle()&quot; title=&quot;关闭&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;img src=&quot;/img/close.jpg&quot;/&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=&quot;shang_tit&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;p&gt;&lt;%=theme.donate_message%&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=&quot;shang_payimg&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;img src=&quot;&lt;%- theme.alipay %&gt;&quot; alt=&quot;扫码支持&quot; title=&quot;扫一扫&quot; width=&quot;168px&quot; height=&quot;168px&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=&quot;pay_explain&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">			扫码打赏，你说多少就多少</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=&quot;shang_payselect&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;label class=&quot;pay_item checked&quot; data-id=&quot;alipay&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;input class=&quot;radiobox&quot; name=&quot;Fruit&quot; type=&quot;radio&quot; checked&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;img src=&quot;/img/alipay.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;支付宝&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;/label&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;label class=&quot;pay_item&quot; data-id=&quot;weipay&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;input class=&quot;radiobox&quot; name=&quot;Fruit&quot; type=&quot;radio&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;img src=&quot;/img/wechat.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;微信支付&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;/label&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=&quot;/js/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;</div><div class="line">$(function()&#123;</div><div class="line">$(&quot;.pay_item&quot;).click(function()&#123;</div><div class="line">    $(this).addClass(&apos;checked&apos;).siblings(&apos;.pay_item&apos;).removeClass(&apos;checked&apos;);</div><div class="line">    var dataid=$(this).attr(&apos;data-id&apos;);</div><div class="line">    if (dataid==&quot;alipay&quot;) &#123;</div><div class="line">        $(&quot;.shang_payimg img&quot;).attr(&quot;src&quot;,&quot;&lt;%- theme.alipay %&gt;&quot;);</div><div class="line">    &#125;;</div><div class="line">    if (dataid==&quot;weipay&quot;) &#123;</div><div class="line">        $(&quot;.shang_payimg img&quot;).attr(&quot;src&quot;,&quot;&lt;%- theme.wechatpay %&gt;&quot;);</div><div class="line">    &#125;;</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div><div class="line">function dashangToggle()&#123;</div><div class="line">    $(&quot;.shang_box&quot;).slideToggle(&quot;fast&quot;);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
