      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js"> </script><p>繁华声 遁入空门 折煞了世人<br>梦偏冷 辗转一生 情债又几本<br>        ……<br>痛直奔 一盏残灯 倾塌的山门<br>听青春 迎来笑声 羡煞许多人<br>那史册 温柔不肯 下笔都太狠</p>
<p><hr><br><div id="aplayer0" class="aplayer" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
		<script>
			new APlayer({
				element: document.getElementById("aplayer0"),
				narrow: false,
				autoplay: true,
				showlrc: 0,
				music: {
					title: "烟花易冷",
					author: "周杰伦",
					url: "http://www.0dutv.com/plug/down/up2.php/1236062.mp3",
